{"tid":1199560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲玩過世紀帝國、三國志？想討論戰術","createTime":"2019-06-10T13:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:22:52.000Z","uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b4dec3497dc08ef6be3d92f78357b6fc6a87d366","tid":1199560,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"其實歷史上，以少勝多嘅戰役。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多數係知自己條team有乜人，可以分成乜人一堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />熟識地型，用自己比較強嘅打對方比較弱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n速度快嘅有法國騎兵喺外圍得閒走下得閒虛攻下，引走對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大隻嘅有印度戰象肉搏，仲有嘅咪英國長弓兵外投，仲有牧師苦口婆心嘅勸告不過多數人地理L你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗外國嘢，中國嘢三國兵法，聲東擊西，暗渡陳倉啊都幾好㗎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一支軍隊咪一大堆一齊，最好就分123456789組，用鄭九組就最好，每段都開戲，爽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n世紀帝國AOC真喺好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />三國志都好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw想去立法局參觀，各位師兄師姐唔知網頁上邊有冇地圖介紹㗎呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好有埋附近點走，可以去埋其他景點嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb792c6fdeeec01af818375334be3b7c8ed99e6","tid":1199560,"uid":150907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9663f926baad0cd8822d7a85cbbe1658679e0f15","tid":1199560,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />10"},{"pid":"57e8780695031039cad3756dfdaa296bb3694f65","tid":1199560,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />9"},{"pid":"b94f61fd74f7113d3470f3134105c6c58c5369fe","tid":1199560,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:04:32.000Z","msg":"無巴絲玩過Aoc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"458b95a763842a0a1f781a6559a25e7199456a69","tid":1199560,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"想瘋狂11 11  11<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef748ac4b42eba0f3f146c523fbe4fb49517c590","tid":1199560,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6795161a4b421589314c5718a09449603ec8dc","tid":1199560,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:10:09.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d956b4f10c66bab4e0f55fc632cce29eb31ed066","tid":1199560,"uid":20546